attributes.title: Barcelona Chair...Knock-Off
attributes.description:
Created on February 24, 2010 by znzn on Sourcemap.org:

47lbs (21.31kg) steel frame with chrome finish
6lbs (2.72kg) leather straps (9mm thick)
10.5lbs (4.76kg) PU foam (foam = 30kg per sq meter)
5.6lbs (2.54kg) leather covers (1.5 oz per sq ft leather)
6.75 (3kg) of steel buttons, rivets, misc. hardware
104' of zippers
351' of piping
